General.Name: Svedbergs i Dalstorp AB (publ)
General.Description: Svedbergs i Dalstorp AB (publ) develops, manufactures, and markets bathroom products in the Nordic countries. The company offers bathroom furniture, including lower parts, mirror cabinet and mirrors, sink, basin mixer, bathroom storage, lighting, and options and handles, as well as storage for laundry room. It also provides showers products, such as corners, partition walls, niche showers, cabins, and optional showers; bathtubs; bath mixers; towel dryers; WC and toilet products; and other bathroom accessories. Svedbergs i Dalstorp AB (publ) was founded in 1920 and is headquartered in Dalstorp, Sweden.
